column5: i dont want to be a burden to anyone, but in the same time i dont want to give my sisters and parents the sadness that i experience. I love them a lot and the thought if committing suicide sounds fine to me since i know how i can kill myself, but my family will have to find my dead body and i just cant give them more problems.
Yeah in my school teachers tell us to take a picture if we don’t have enough time to write everything down, sadly, it’s not the same with every teacher ;(
